                <value><![CDATA[Weaponcrafting usually uses less components than armorcrafting so it is cheaper to master.  Although you may not make as much money with it as armocrafting, you will eventually be able to make some powerful weapons when you start imbueing and adding jewels. 

Recipes
--------------
Axes:
*Hand Axe*
  - 4 Ingots

Bladed Weapons:
*Dagger*               
  - 2 Ingots
*Longsword*         
  - 6 Ingots

Blunt Weapons:
*Mace*                  
  - 3 Ingots

Exotic:
*Kama*                  
  - 2 Ingots

Tools:
*Smithing Hammer* 
  - 4 Ingots
*Pickaxe*               
  - 5 Ingots
*Skinning Knife*      
  - 3 Ingots

